parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the xenon ballast can cause the headlights to flicker or shut off, leading to reduced visibility and increased risk of accidents, especially at night.
symptoms: The headlights flicker or shut off
the "dipped headlight" error message appears on the dashboard
the headlights may turn off and on intermittently
and the problem may occur more frequently in cold weather or when driving over bumps.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can lead to serious injury or death in the event of a crash, as the airbag may not deploy or may deploy incorrectly.
symptoms: The airbag warning light stays on
the airbag does not deploy in a crash
the passenger airbag deploys when the driver airbag does not
no warning chime for unbuckled seatbelts.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The delay or failure to repair the Takata airbag recall can lead to serious injury or death in the event of a crash, as the airbag may not deploy or may deploy incorrectly.
symptoms: The airbag warning light stays on
the airbag does not deploy in a crash
the passenger airbag deploys when the driver airbag does not
no warning chime for unbuckled seatbelts
delay or failure to receive recall repairs.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the seatbelt warning chime can lead to occupants not buckling up, increasing the risk of injury or death in the event of a crash.
symptoms: No warning chime for unbuckled seatbelts.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The intermittent failure of the headlights can cause a serious safety concern, especially when driving at night, and may lead to accidents or traffic violations.
symptoms: The headlights flicker or turn off randomly
sometimes with an error message displaying "Left" or "Right" dipped headlight
and may require the headlights to be turned off and back on to restore function.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Excessive engine oil consumption can lead to premature engine wear, potentially causing engine failure, and may also lead to environmental damage.
symptoms: The engine oil level drops rapidly
requiring frequent oil changes
and may be accompanied by other engine-related issues.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Ignition coil failure can cause the engine to stall or misfire, leading to a loss of power and potentially causing accidents.
symptoms: The engine may stall or misfire
and may be accompanied by a burning smell or smoke.
